WEBVTT

00:02:27.563 --> 00:02:30.326
I could have PMS, you could have PMS,

00:02:30.326 --> 00:02:32.880
the guy in the third row here
could have PMS,

00:02:32.880 --> 00:02:35.573
my dog could have PMS.
(Laughter)

00:02:36.193 --> 00:02:38.861
Some researchers said
you had to have five symptoms.

00:02:38.861 --> 00:02:40.426
Some said three.

00:02:40.426 --> 00:02:43.282
Other researchers said that symptoms
were only meaningful

00:02:43.282 --> 00:02:45.116
if they were highly disturbing to you,

00:02:45.116 --> 00:02:48.669
but others said minor symptoms
were just as important.

00:02:48.669 --> 00:02:51.571
For many years, because
there was no standardization

00:02:51.571 --> 00:02:53.660
in the definition of PMS,

00:02:53.660 --> 00:02:56.725
when psychologists tried
to report prevalence rates,

00:02:56.725 --> 00:02:59.512
their estimates ranged
from five percent of women

00:02:59.512 --> 00:03:01.810
to 97 percent of women,